text: Edit Sipos (2 March 1975 in Szentes - 13 August 2013) is a Hungarian water polo player. She competed for the Hungarian women's national water polo team for 150 caps. She played in the 2001 World Aquatics Championships and 2001 European Water polo Championships. == References == Category:1975 births Category:2013 deaths Category:Hungarian water polo players
